Accept: application/json

###

# Chat API Requests

### 1. Create a new chat session
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Conversation"
}

###

### 2. Send a message to the session (replace {sessionId} with the ID from step 1)
# @name sendMessage
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "how are you?"
}

###

### 3. Get all messages from the session
GET {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}/messages
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get all sessions
GET {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Stream a message (real-time response)
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Tell me a short story"
}

###

### 6. Delete a session
DELETE {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/chat/sessions/{sessionId}
